verbose_text: Surfactant protein-B (SPB) and alpha-SMA expression patterns were evaluated using immunohistochemistry, and the protein levels of nuclear transcription factor NF-E2-related factor 2 (Nrf-2) and its associated antioxidant enzymes heme oxygenase-1 enzyme (HO-1) and NAD (P) H : quinone oxidoreductase-1 (NQO-1) were examined via western blot analysis.
evidence: levels of nuclear transcription factor NF-E2-related factor 2
